      <title>绿柱石正在恢复强度，有望以飓风形式抵达德克萨斯州</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-07/beryl-regaining-strength-on-track-to-reach-texas-as-hurricane</link>
      <description><![CDATA[热带风暴贝丽尔 (Beryl) 缓慢向德克萨斯州南部海岸移动，强度不断增强，预计将在周一凌晨登陆前再次成为飓风。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-07/beryl-regaining-strength-on-track-to-reach-texas-as-hurricane</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 16:07:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Apple Watch 的下一步：屏幕更大但外观相似</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-07-07/apple-watch-series-10-ultra-3-details-bigger-screens-blood-pressure-challenge-lybjqp0q</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着 Apple Watch 即将迎来 10 周年纪念，该公司正在准备进行重大更新。此外：带摄像头的 AirPods 再次成为新闻焦点，苹果获得了 OpenAI 董事会观察员席位。]]></description>
